<p>para. 30; <i>May v. Ferndale Institution</i>, [2005] 3 S.C.R. 809, para. 76; <i>Kindler v. Canada</i> (Minister of 
Justice), [1991] 2 S.C.R. 779, p, 831; <i>Cunningham v. Canada</i>, [1993] 2 S.C.R. 143, pp. 148&#8211;151); 
United States of America (Restatement (Third) of Foreign Relations Law, section 702 (1987), and <i>Ma 
v. Ashcroft</i>, 257 F.3d 1095, 1114 (9th Cir. 2001); <i>Martinez v. City of Los Angeles</i>, 141 F.3d 1373, 
1384 (9th Cir. 1998); and <i>De Sanchez v. Banco Central de Nicaragua</i>, 770 F.2d 1385, 1397 (5th Cir. 
1985)); see also submission by the Government of Lithuania. 
