</p>
<p>March 2006, para. 9.6; <i>Bandajevsky v. Belarus</i>, communication No. 1100/2002, Views adopted on 28 
March 2006, para. 10.3; <i>Borisenko v. Hungary</i>, communication No. 852/1999, Views adopted on 14 
October 2002, para. 7.4. 
</p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>37
 See <i>Brogan and Others v. The United Kingdom (application 11209/84; 11234/84; 11266/84; 
</i></p>
<p><i>11386/85), Judgement</i>, para. 62. 
 
</p>
<p>38
